flowchart TB
  %% Data Migration Flow Template
  %% ETL process for large-scale data migration

  Start((Migration Start)) --> PlanningPhase[Planning Phase]

  PlanningPhase --> DataAssessment[Data Assessment & Profiling]
  DataAssessment --> MappingDesign[Field Mapping Design]
  MappingDesign --> ValidationRules[Validation Rules Definition]

  ValidationRules --> PreMigrationReady{Ready for Migration?}

  PreMigrationReady -->|No| RefinePlan[Refine Plan]
  PreMigrationReady -->|Yes| BackupSource[Backup Source System]

  RefinePlan --> DataAssessment

  BackupSource --> ExtractPhase[Extract Phase]

  subgraph Extraction["Data Extraction"]
    ExtractPhase --> QuerySource[Query Source Data]
    QuerySource --> DeduplicationCheck[Deduplication Check]
    DeduplicationCheck --> ExportCSV[Export to Staging CSV]
  end

  ExportCSV --> TransformPhase[Transform Phase]

  subgraph Transformation["Data Transformation"]
    TransformPhase --> FieldMapping[Apply Field Mappings]
    FieldMapping --> DataCleansing[Data Cleansing]
    DataCleansing --> EnrichmentRules[Apply Enrichment Rules]
    EnrichmentRules --> ValidationChecks[Validation Checks]
  end

  ValidationChecks --> ValidationResult{All Records Valid?}

  ValidationResult -->|No| ErrorHandling[Error Handling]
  ValidationResult -->|Yes| LoadPhase[Load Phase]

  ErrorHandling --> ReviewErrors[Review Error Records]
  ReviewErrors --> FixErrors{Fix and Retry?}
  FixErrors -->|Yes| TransformPhase
  FixErrors -->|No| QuarantineRecords[Quarantine Records]

  subgraph Loading["Data Loading"]
    LoadPhase --> BatchProcessing[Batch Processing]
    BatchProcessing --> LoadToTarget[Load to Target System]
    LoadToTarget --> CheckResults{Load Successful?}
    CheckResults -->|Partial Success| RetryFailed[Retry Failed Records]
    CheckResults -->|Full Failure| RollbackDecision{Rollback?}
    RetryFailed --> CheckResults
    RollbackDecision -->|Yes| ExecuteRollback[Execute Rollback]
    RollbackDecision -->|No| DocumentFailure[Document Failure]
  end

  CheckResults -->|Full Success| PostMigrationValidation[Post-Migration Validation]

  PostMigrationValidation --> ReconciliationCheck[Reconciliation Check]
  ReconciliationCheck --> DataIntegrityTest[Data Integrity Tests]
  DataIntegrityTest --> SmokeTests[Smoke Tests]

  SmokeTests --> ValidationPassed{Validation Passed?}

  ValidationPassed -->|No| InvestigateIssues[Investigate Issues]
  ValidationPassed -->|Yes| EnableIntegrations[Enable Integrations]

  InvestigateIssues --> FixIssues{Issues Resolved?}
  FixIssues -->|No| RollbackDecision
  FixIssues -->|Yes| PostMigrationValidation

  EnableIntegrations --> CleanupStaging[Cleanup Staging Data]
  CleanupStaging --> DocumentMigration[Document Migration Results]

  DocumentMigration --> Complete((Migration Complete))
  QuarantineRecords --> Complete
  ExecuteRollback --> Complete
  DocumentFailure --> Complete

  %% Styling
  style ExtractPhase fill:#4A90E2
  style TransformPhase fill:#4A90E2
  style LoadPhase fill:#4A90E2
  style ErrorHandling fill:#F5A623
  style ExecuteRollback fill:#D0021B
  style Complete fill:#7ED321
